= Installation instructions =

The~installation of~LUWRAIN on~your PC can be~performed in~several ways.
It~depends on~whether you'd like to~get LUWRAIN as~a~stand-alone OS or as~an~application.
In~second case it~also depends on~the~type of~OS 
you have installed on~your PC.

== Select the~way you'd like to~continue with: ==

* Install LUWRAIN as~a~stand-alone OS
* Install LUWRAIN as~an~application for:
** Microsoft Windows
** [local:linux/ GNU/Linux]

